{"prompt": "Create a professional website for a law firm. The design should be sophisticated, using a gamboge yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Gilded Scales Law Firm</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #e4a31d; /* Gamboge yellow */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #a07213 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        header nav {\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        header nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            padding: 5px 10px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        header nav a:hover {\n            background-color: #a07213; /* Darker gamboge for hover */\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(228, 163, 29, 0.7), rgba(228, 163, 29, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/f0f0f0/ffffff?text=Law+Firm+Background') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 500px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #e4a31d; /* Gamboge yellow */\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #e4a31d;\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        #about .col-2 {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 40px;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        #about .col-2 div {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n        #services .row {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 30px;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 280px;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #e4a31d; /* Gamboge yellow */\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        #contact {\n            background-color: #e4a31d; /* Gamboge yellow */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        #contact textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        #contact button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #a07213; /* Darker gamboge */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            header nav {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                gap: 10px;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            #about .col-2 {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .service-item {\n                min-width: unset;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Gilded Scales Law Firm</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n                <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\" class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Excellence. Integrity. Justice.</h2>\n            <p>Your trusted legal advocates, dedicated to achieving your objectives.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Our Firm</h2>\n            <div class=\"col-2\">\n                <div>\n                    <p>Gilded Scales Law Firm is a premier legal practice committed to providing unparalleled legal counsel and representation. With a deep understanding of various legal domains and a client-centric approach, we strive to deliver effective and tailored solutions.</p>\n                    <p>Our team of seasoned attorneys brings a wealth of experience, dedication, and a sharp analytical mind to every case. We believe in building strong relationships with our clients, grounded in trust and clear communication.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/e4a31d/ffffff?text=Lawyers\" alt=\"Lawyers\" style=\"width:100%; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Practice Areas</h2>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Navigating complex business transactions and regulatory landscapes with expertise.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Litigation</h3>\n                    <p>Aggressively representing clients in civil and commercial disputes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Real Estate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Providing comprehensive legal support for property transactions and disputes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n                    <p>Protecting your innovations and creative works with robust legal strategies.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>We are here to assist you. Please reach out with your legal inquiries.</p>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Gilded Scales Law Firm. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message Sent! Thank you for reaching out.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}